OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBritish Sign Language to be
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fintroduced as GCSE         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, British Sign Language (BSL) will be    
OL,6, taught as a GCSE in England from       
OL,7, September 2025, the government says.   
OL,9,FIt says the qualification will be open 
OL,10,Fto all pupils, who will learn about    
OL,11,F1,000 signs, as well as an important   
OL,12,Flife skill and advance inclusivity.    
OL,14,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan said
OL,15,Fthe subject will "open so many doors   
OL,16,Ffor young people".                     
OL,18,FThe exams regulator Ofqual will review 
OL,19,Fand accredit the syllabus before it can
OL,20,Fbe taught in schools and colleges.     
